@Lazarus38611569 @LKrauss1 Either we expand to the stars or we wait around on Earth until a natural or manmade extinction event occurs. 

Those are our choices. 

Also, being multiplanetary greatly improves the probability that we can intercept a meteor headed for Earth or otherwise come to the rescue!

